bodyEn:
Subject: Follow-up — Failed UPI P2M Transaction — 30 days elapsed — UTR {UTR}

To: {BANK_NAME} Nodal Officer,

Reference: complaint ref {TICKET_NO} dated {COMPLAINT_DATE} regarding failed UPI P2M transaction of Rs. {AMOUNT} (UTR {UTR}) on {TXN_DATE}.

30 days have passed without resolution. Daily Rs. 100 compensation meter is active.

Total compensation due today: Rs. {COMPENSATION_DUE}.

Resolve within 48 hours, or I will approach NPCI and the RBI Ombudsman under RB-IOS 2026.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
